     LEFT JOIN VIEWpagosPRCMA d ON a.numfactu = d.numfactu  
       WHERE
       a.fechafac ='10/18/2019' AND   a.cod_subgrupo = 'CONSULTA' and  a.statfact=3  and d.desTipoTargeta is  not null and a.usuario='YFELICIANO' 
       GROUP BY  
       desTipoTargeta  
       Order by 
       desTipoTargeta
